    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Ruf</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Lucilius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cam</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> Au<lb break="no" n="3"/><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>usta</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Apol</abbr><ex>linaris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Lucilius <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>po</abbr><ex>suit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Zeile 1 kleines S am Zeilenende. Die origo ist Augusta Bagiennorum (bei Bene Vagienna, Piedmont). Zeile 6 aufgrund des nomen wohl f(ilio), möglicherweise jedoch auch f(rater). Über dem Inschriftfeld Nische mit Vollfigur in tunica, paenula und caligae; am Gürtel pugio und gladius. Das cognomen steht hier an der Stelle des praenomen. Z. 6: f(ilio) oder f(rater). (B): Z. 4: Krüger: XXXI.</p>
            </div>
